column5: Hello everyone, I'm planning to go fishing on lake Simcoe this weekend. However, I need you guys help me to find a boat rental place. Daily rate around $100 and under would be great. and they should still in bussiness, I've got some cheap rates one but they're no longer in bussiness.   Thanks in advance.
can't really help you as i don't rent out of simcoe, but just wanted to say that if your avatar is of your fish, then you have a gorgeous short finned betta!
saw a pontoon one time in cooks with a phone number 705 456 3131 try calling and see what they have to offer.
Harry's Bait and Tackle in Keswick rents boats.  905-476-0441
Hi guys, Thanks all for the info, I've called around and this is the most decent one. It's the lakesimcoemarine.com  FISH ONNNNNN
